column5: LOL! Can you show us what a juiced skeeter looks like next?
Most people would take them back for the core refund
You see........if that was a original Toyota battery, the press would of broke...................

You know I have that exact energizer I bought from Wally mart, in 2008, and it still works like a charm (outlasted my deka's!).  Anybody know of a place which will give me cash for about 5 crapped out boat batteries?....I know u get core on trade in, but I just need to rid of the batteries.    Anyways, it hurts to see that in the press, I assume it let you down when you needed it most!
It was probably getting too friendly with the weed whacker.
Everyone on the board should take up a collection of gobies and send them to whitespinnerbait. Squish them a dozen at a time in clear plastic containers.
Cool! But...   I'll see your crusher and raise you one shredder. The fun really gets going at around the 0:58 mark:  http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Aja7gcgRMJU
